Because if there
were, that would

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:43.920
have made A
transpose A singular,

00:04:43.920 --> 00:04:48.650
and we would have had to
do something different.

00:04:48.650 --> 00:04:52.100
Here, this'll be a
lot like this one.

00:04:52.100 --> 00:04:59.370
Today, once you see A, you'll
